OL,3,CSignificant shortfalls found in green
OL,4,Cenergy strategy implementation
OL,6,FProgress with Northern Ireland's
OL,7,Fenergy strategy is "lagging
OL,8,Fconsiderably", an Audit Office report
OL,9,Fhas found.
OL,11,FThe ambition plan, launched in 2021,
OL,12,Faimed to achieve 80% of the region's
OL,13,Felectricity from renewable sources by
OL,14,F2030, using wind and solar sources.
OL,16,FEnergy Strategy ` Path To Net Zero
OL,17,FEnergy also referred to a vision of
OL,18,Fnet zero carbon and affordable energy
OL,19,Fby 2050.
