OL,3,CSignificant shortfalls found in green
OL,4,Cenergy strategy implementation
OL,6,FHowever a new report from Comptroller
OL,7,Fand Auditor General Dorinnia Carville,
OL,8,Fsaid progress against key targets in
OL,9,Fthe strategy is "lagging considerably".
OL,11,FThe report found this was despite
OL,12,Fexpenditure totalling around #107
OL,13,Fmillion since 2020.
OL,15,FIt considered the strategy and also
OL,16,Fevaluated the approach taken by the
OL,17,FDepartment for the Economy to
OL,18,Fimplement it.
