OL,3,CSignificant shortfalls found in green
OL,4,Cenergy strategy implementation
OL,6,FOf three key targets for completion by
OL,7,F2030, the report found "significant
OL,8,Fshortfalls" in relation to two of
OL,9,Fthese.
OL,11,FThese include a target to save a total
OL,12,Fof 8,000 GWh of energy savings by
OL,13,F2030. Just 90 GWh of savings were
OL,14,Freported in March 2025 (around 1% of
OL,15,Fthe target).
OL,17,FAnd against a target of at least 80%
OL,18,Fof electricity consumption from
OL,19,Frenewable sources, the amount reported
OL,20,Fin March was 45%.
