OL,3,CSignificant shortfalls found in green
OL,4,Cenergy strategy implementation
OL,6,FThese include a "lack of clarity"
OL,7,Faround planned actions and a "lack of
OL,8,Fprecise detail" on when some actions
OL,9,Fwould be completed, the actual work
OL,10,Fplanned, or specific and measurable
OL,11,Foutcomes.
OL,13,FA lack of interim targets or
OL,14,Fmilestones in the strategy to help
OL,15,Fdetermine the pace of progress towards
OL,16,Fmeeting key targets was noted.
