OL,6,FMeanwhile the report also flagged that
OL,7,Fthe monitoring of some targets by the
OL,8,Fgroup tasked with oversight (the
OL,9,FEnergy Strategy Oversight Group) only
OL,10,Ftook place for the first time in
OL,11,FSeptember 2024, almost three years
OL,12,Fafter the strategy was published.
OL,14,FMs Carville said she was concerned
OL,15,Fabout the shortcomings in good
OL,16,Fgovernance and oversight identified in
OL,17,Fthe report.
