OL,6,F"The Energy Strategy has a pivotal
OL,7,Frole in ensuring Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fmeets its ambitions and obligations in
OL,9,Frelation to net zero, energy
OL,10,Fefficiency and tackling climate
OL,11,Fchange," she said.
OL,13,F"Successful implementation requires
OL,14,Fgood governance and effective
OL,15,Foversight, and this report highlights
OL,16,Fconcerning shortcomings in these areas.
