OL,6,F"It has been difficult to assess
OL,7,Fwhether the significant expenditure
OL,8,Fincurred to date represents value for
OL,9,Fmoney, and there is a risk that key
OL,10,Ftargets will not be met.
OL,12,F"We welcome more recent changes to the
OL,13,FDepartment's reporting arrangements,
OL,14,Fwhich will help provide greater
OL,15,Fclarity.
OL,17,F"The Department committed to carrying
OL,18,Fout a strategic update review of the
OL,19,FEnergy Strategy in 2025.
